textAnnotations.description:
Men LOCAL BUS DISAPPEARS announced the
Dinas Advertiser. But the London papers ignored
the whole affair. I for Evans reported his loss
to the police. But they only tuttutted. "Lost
careless.
Very careless." That was their
a bas, is it. Very
attitude. Now if there'd been a good old accident,
they could have measured up the road and
taken an interest.
